Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,//--------------------OPCN---------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.16,0:00:33.97,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}「いま！」という　この瞬間
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.97,0:00:39.40,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}なんだって　音楽に　出来たらいいのに
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.40,0:00:44.18,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}まだ　全力で　やり切ってない
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.18,0:00:46.90,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}悔し涙　拭ったんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.90,0:00:50.43,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}青春のフレージング
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.43,0:00:55.46,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}奇跡が　努力の　先にあるなら
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.66,0:01:01.15,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}限界は　あたしが決める
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.15,0:01:03.31,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}響け
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.31,0:01:10.17,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}もう一回　大げさな夢を　探しにいこう
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.17,0:01:13.78,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}止めない　勇気こそ　強さ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.78,0:01:20.57,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}何百回　挑戦かさねて　ここまで来た
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.57,0:01:24.97,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}チャンスの神様　みててね
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.97,0:01:27.55,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}忘れたくないメロディ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.55,0:01:30.22,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}離したくないメロディ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.22,0:01:33.25,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}輝きに変えて
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.91,0:01:38.28,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}想いよ　届け…！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.16,0:00:33.97,OPCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}「此时此刻」的这个瞬间
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.97,0:00:39.40,OPCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}希望能以音乐将其铭刻
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.40,0:00:44.18,OPCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}还未拼尽全力到最后
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.18,0:00:46.90,OPCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}不断拭去的悔恨泪水
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.90,0:00:50.43,OPCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}是青春的分句
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.43,0:00:55.46,OPCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}若是努力之后便会有奇迹
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.66,0:01:01.15,OPCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}那极限由我来决定
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.15,0:01:03.31,OPCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}吹响吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.31,0:01:10.17,OPCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}再一次去追寻那庞大的梦想
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.17,0:01:13.78,OPCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}强大就是永不放弃的勇气
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.78,0:01:20.57,OPCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}经历数百次的挑战　来到这里
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.57,0:01:24.97,OPCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}请机会之神看好了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.97,0:01:27.55,OPCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}不想忘记的旋律
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.55,0:01:30.22,OPCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}不愿放开的旋律
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.22,0:01:33.25,OPCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}变为耀眼的光辉
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.91,0:01:38.28,OPCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}将这份心意　传递出去…！
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,--------------------PART--------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.02,0:00:02.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,若是本周末前
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.98,0:00:06.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还不能确定田中同学能继续参加社团活动
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.61,0:00:12.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我将会让中川同学代替她出场全国大赛
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.99,0:01:48.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,黄前…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.83,0:01:51.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夏纪学姐
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.60,0:01:56.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然由我来吹会觉得不安？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.91,0:02:00.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不…没那回事…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.00,0:02:02.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我很不安
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.45,0:02:07.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你什么时候知道这事的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.74,0:02:12.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在明日香学姐的妈妈来学校后没多久
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.61,0:02:15.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明日香学姐对我说的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.56,0:02:24.38,Title,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(1040,720)\bord1.5\blur2\fad(500,0)}吹响吧!悠风号
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.37,0:02:26.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接下来会怎么样呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.62,0:02:29.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这就要看明日香学姐了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.97,0:02:31.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,毕竟是她的父母
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.38,0:02:34.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,周围的人胡乱插嘴只会让事情更糟
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.65,0:02:35.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说得也是
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.18,0:02:39.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我觉得泷老师的决定是正确的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.33,0:02:44.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,若是大家继续这样动摇下去是没有好处的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.98,0:02:48.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明日香学姐真不在乎被人替代吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.34,0:02:50.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,久美子…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.80,0:02:54.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,泷老师说这是她同意的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.94,0:02:58.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明日香学姐你不会退部的吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.80,0:03:03.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不会退部的吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.88,0:03:04.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,放心吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.16,0:03:07.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不会做出那种让大家为难的决定的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.40,0:03:11.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在说什么呢  今天可不是最后
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.42,0:03:14.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们可是要去全国大赛的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.63,0:03:19.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,久美子…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.79,0:03:22.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么你看上去那么心烦呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.14,0:03:28.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为不甘心
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.82,0:03:29.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么不甘心
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.57,0:03:31.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不知道…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.89,0:03:37.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我回来了…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.52,0:03:42.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,姐姐…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.38,0:03:51.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好  那么再来一遍
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.19,0:03:53.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,3  4
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.58,0:04:00.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明日香学姐第二天的练习也没有来
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.48,0:04:03.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夏纪学姐的乐谱上
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.72,0:04:07.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有着许多明日香学姐写下的建议
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.14,0:04:10.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\b1\bord0\1c&H7E5BEB&\frx0\fry3\frz22\pos(880,308)}向着全国大赛呐喊!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.42,0:04:13.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就像是遗言一般
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.40,0:04:14.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我如此觉得
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.08,0:04:18.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.52,0:04:23.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,带回明日香学姐大作战？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.96,0:04:24.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.10,0:04:26.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是什么作战啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.82,0:04:31.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,话说在前面  作战名是香织学姐定的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.63,0:04:34.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是好棒的作战名呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.34,0:04:40.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,黄前你下周不是要到明日香学姐家里去学习吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.36,0:04:40.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我做不到
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.76,0:04:43.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我还什么都没说呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.92,0:04:47.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是想让我借机说服她妈妈吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.26,0:04:49.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.24,0:04:51.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,做不到的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.28,0:04:53.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别强人所难了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.78,0:04:54.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,放心吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.16,0:04:57.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,香织学姐给了我好建议
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.52,0:05:03.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,车站前幸富堂的栗子馒头是我最推荐的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.88,0:05:05.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.96,0:05:08.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,据说明日香学姐的妈妈非常喜欢吃
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.55,0:05:11.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要带上这个就万事OK
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.40,0:05:14.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你看着我的眼睛再说一遍
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.75,0:05:15.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,OK…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.76,0:05:21.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过  你总是能把事情圆满解决
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.55,0:05:25.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,无论是高坂同学的时候  还是霙的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.38,0:05:27.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我什么都没做…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.76,0:05:28.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有那回事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.06,0:05:32.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你觉得明日香学姐为什么会叫你去她家？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.80,0:05:34.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.41,0:05:41.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我觉得是因为她在期待你能帮助到她
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.00,0:05:43.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有那回事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.84,0:05:46.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且  若是因此明日香学姐回归的话
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.44,0:05:49.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你就不能吹奏了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.62,0:05:54.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我没关系  我还有明年
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.48,0:05:57.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在对这个部来说最好的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.76,0:05:59.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是由明日香学姐来吹奏
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.86,0:06:05.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是你的真心话吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.64,0:06:09.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是黄前风格的提问呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.60,0:06:12.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  是我的真心话
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.76,0:06:16.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夏纪
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.42,0:06:18.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,结束了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.84,0:06:21.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我都说了我会去找你们的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.52,0:06:25.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,希美学姐  铠冢学姐
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.86,0:06:30.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我希望你能替我们转告明日香学姐
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.70,0:06:32.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们等着她
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.48,0:06:40.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.74,0:06:42.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们说了这些事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.80,0:06:43.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.80,0:06:45.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,责任重大啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.29,0:06:51.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,丽奈你觉得明日香学姐为什么会叫我去她家？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.82,0:06:53.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我和你在不同组
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.90,0:06:56.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对明日香学姐不怎么了解
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.38,0:06:58.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说得也是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.16,0:07:01.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过  感觉自己能明白一点
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.10,0:07:05.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,久美子你有些与众不同
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.34,0:07:10.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看似平平常常  却感觉看透了本质
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.92,0:07:14.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看似毫无察觉  却感觉洞悉了一切
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.44,0:07:16.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这算什么
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.98,0:07:21.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后  在一切位于最痛处的时候语出惊人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.02,0:07:27.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,「你真的觉得我们能参加全国大赛吗」
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.48,0:07:32.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是…那个时候…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.30,0:07:35.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以  感觉你有些与众不同
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.66,0:07:40.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想一下子抓住你  把你的那层外皮剥掉
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.56,0:07:43.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明日香学姐也是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.14,0:07:48.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.48,0:07:53.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,打扰了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.10,0:07:56.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老师
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.87,0:07:59.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,睡着了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.02,0:08:01.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,毕竟从早上到现在
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.16,0:08:04.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,比所有人都要早到
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.48,0:08:06.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看着大家练习…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.48,0:08:10.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,叫醒他的话就太可怜了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.21,0:08:12.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把钥匙放下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.04,0:08:13.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.76,0:08:19.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.96,0:08:22.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,黄前同学
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.56,0:08:26.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,高坂同学
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.20,0:08:31.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉  让你们看见了我慵懒的一面
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.14,0:08:33.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,丽奈
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.94,0:08:38.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,感谢您平时的指导
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.74,0:08:40.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我来还钥匙了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.25,0:08:42.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.72,0:08:46.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不用…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.80,0:08:50.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对了  黄前同学
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.41,0:08:51.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.34,0:08:54.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要是觉得中川同学的演奏有哪里要改进
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.30,0:08:56.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请和她直说
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.02,0:09:00.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我觉得中川同学也希望你能告诉她
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.64,0:09:02.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.80,0:09:06.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后  自选曲158小节开始
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.31,0:09:09.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你做好一个人吹奏的心理准备
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.20,0:09:11.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好的…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.92,0:09:18.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最坏的打算  要一个人吹吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.24,0:09:36.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,终于到了去明日香学姐家的日子了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.66,0:09:38.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在那
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.64,0:09:42.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,黄前
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.89,0:09:45.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是什么书啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.86,0:09:46.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你很好奇？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.66,0:09:50.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那如果有趣的话  我就借给你
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.60,0:09:52.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.77,0:09:55.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.12,0:09:59.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很久没这种时间回家了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.12,0:10:00.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.34,0:10:04.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  不过之前因为感冒  练习有请过假
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.08,0:10:05.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.38,0:10:06.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.68,0:10:08.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.20,0:10:12.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我连这种事也不知道了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.47,0:10:18.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对了  明日香学姐的家在哪呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.78,0:10:20.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很近哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.04,0:10:23.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很平时骑自行车差不多10分钟吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.91,0:10:25.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.46,0:10:29.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对话进行不下去
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.30,0:10:30.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.04,0:10:32.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.39,0:10:34.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这双运动鞋
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.96,0:10:35.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很可爱吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.14,0:10:37.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  确实
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.45,0:10:41.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正好碰巧有我的尺寸
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.58,0:10:42.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为我脚比较大…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.28,0:10:43.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs50\bord2.5\fsp3}明日香
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.42,0:10:47.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,香织
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.10,0:10:50.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.33,0:10:53.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看到你的背影…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.22,0:10:56.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就追上来了…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.22,0:10:58.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,黄前
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.06,0:10:59.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.26,0:11:02.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不介意我和你们一起走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.36,0:11:04.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当然了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.22,0:11:08.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那确实有点问题呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.56,0:11:10.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我和晴香也说过了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.16,0:11:14.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们打算在组长会议上听取下意见
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.07,0:11:16.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦  这主意挺好的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.52,0:11:17.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.64,0:11:18.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.66,0:11:18.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.20,0:11:22.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我还要去别的地方就先走了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.08,0:11:25.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,黄前同学  这个给你
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.94,0:11:30.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,学习会需要茶点吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.77,0:11:31.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以收下吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.14,0:11:32.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.26,0:11:35.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那明日香的事就拜托你了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.76,0:11:38.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天是我帮助她补习吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.79,0:11:42.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明日香  你鞋带松了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.11,0:11:45.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你还是系不好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.46,0:11:49.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看  这样系就不容易松开了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.27,0:11:56.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.33,0:11:58.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不客气
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.50,0:11:59.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再见
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.41,0:12:00.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.98,0:12:02.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.98,0:12:07.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很可爱吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.24,0:12:08.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,埃？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.09,0:12:09.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,香织
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.42,0:12:16.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里就是我家
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.26,0:12:19.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,家里没有人  不用客气
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.32,0:12:27.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给  请喝
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.03,0:12:29.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有劳了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.16,0:12:34.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很紧张吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.20,0:12:35.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.20,0:12:39.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你把悠风号带回家了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.63,0:12:43.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过是瞒着那个人的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.65,0:12:49.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对了  这个玻璃杯是我生日时香织送给我的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.80,0:12:51.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.01,0:12:56.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么让我看一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.28,0:12:57.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.01,0:12:58.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的笔记
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.93,0:13:02.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拜托你了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.41,0:13:02.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.18,0:13:11.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这位小姐…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.43,0:13:11.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.32,0:13:15.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你这水平可是重症级别的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.64,0:13:17.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.23,0:13:20.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把这里和这里加起来
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.61,0:13:22.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原来如此
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.79,0:13:25.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对对  就是这样  黄前
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.25,0:13:28.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,稍微休息一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.02,0:13:31.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要吃那个栗子馒头吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.50,0:13:35.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊…这个是送给您妈妈的…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.24,0:13:37.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然是这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.31,0:13:40.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,确实是香织会想出来的主意
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.87,0:13:41.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  这…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.16,0:13:43.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.77,0:13:47.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很遗憾  我妈妈今天回家会很晚
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.70,0:13:50.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我姑且会转交给她的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.90,0:13:51.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拿来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.39,0:13:55.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拜托你了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.73,0:13:57.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多谢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.86,0:14:00.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我再去泡点茶
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.87,0:14:02.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也来帮忙
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.80,0:14:06.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,脚麻了…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.48,0:14:11.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没什么好东西呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.88,0:14:12.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,饼干可以吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.82,0:14:16.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个…能问你一个问题吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.56,0:14:16.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.55,0:14:20.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么突然要帮我补习呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.01,0:14:26.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为我听闻你的成绩不是一点点差
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.13,0:14:29.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谁…是谁说的！？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.09,0:14:30.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,开玩笑的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.60,0:14:32.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.35,0:14:34.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想和你聊聊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.77,0:14:38.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这本书你有看过吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.26,0:14:39.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看过
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.40,0:14:41.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也有一本
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.60,0:14:45.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最开始学大部分人都用的这本书吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.93,0:14:51.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这本书的作者  名为进藤正和的悠风号演奏家
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.54,0:14:53.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他很有名的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.48,0:14:55.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我还有他的CD
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.72,0:14:57.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,曾经是我的父亲
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.63,0:15:01.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,红茶要涼了  快喝吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.53,0:15:04.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,学姐  现在可不是喝茶的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.58,0:15:06.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,提问时间
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.06,0:15:08.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个…首先
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.06,0:15:10.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,曾经是父亲是什么意思？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.24,0:15:14.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这很显而易见吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.50,0:15:15.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我父母离婚了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.96,0:15:19.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以我才叫田中明日香
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.96,0:15:20.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.80,0:15:23.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们在我2岁的时候就离婚了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.50,0:15:26.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以我对父亲没有什么印象
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.98,0:15:32.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从那以后就没和父亲见过面吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.38,0:15:35.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我妈妈呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.22,0:15:38.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,似乎非常不想我和他扯上关系
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.01,0:15:42.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你那时在办公室也有看到吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.46,0:15:45.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她那人有点奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.56,0:15:46.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奇怪…？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.70,0:15:50.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,占有欲很强  动不动就歇斯底里
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.10,0:15:54.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说不定我父亲就是受不了这点才离开的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.72,0:16:00.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过  我并不讨厌她
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.25,0:16:03.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,毕竟是她把我抚养长大的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.82,0:16:06.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是我欠她的  所以内心还是想着要报答的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.46,0:16:11.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然你嘴上说不讨厌她
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.43,0:16:15.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其实内心是讨厌她的吧…？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.08,0:16:19.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这不是喜欢讨厌的问题
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.58,0:16:23.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为母亲无论到哪都是自己的母亲
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.44,0:16:28.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不管发生什么  你是她生的这点不会改变
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.90,0:16:32.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就像是枷锁  一生都无法去下的枷锁
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.91,0:16:38.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她的心中有自己的一套幸福蓝图
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.90,0:16:40.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而吹奏乐在那并无一席之地
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.36,0:16:43.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从一开始就没
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.12,0:16:45.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那你为什么还要开始吹悠风号
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.70,0:16:48.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是在小学一年级的时候吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.38,0:16:50.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我突然收到了一个包裹
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.14,0:16:53.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\bord0\b0\1c&H9A9D9B&\fs60\frz349\pos(1196,912)}给 明 日 香
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.62,0:16:54.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\bord0\b0\1c&H9A9D9B&\fs60\frz348\move(1196,912,1196,2012,15,2000)}给 明 日 香
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.72,0:16:53.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,里面是破旧的笔记  一封信
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.66,0:16:55.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有悠风号
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.70,0:16:59.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,之后不久
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.66,0:17:03.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我听说附近的乐器店有位店员曾经吹奏过悠风号
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.41,0:17:07.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去试了之后  没想到还吹得不错
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.75,0:17:12.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这让我非常地高兴
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.13,0:17:14.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,像漫画一般的故事呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.10,0:17:19.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过  那个人自然是反对我吹的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.81,0:17:22.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一开始  她还能容忍
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.35,0:17:26.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但见我不打算放弃  就和我大吵了一架
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.29,0:17:31.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最后约定要是成绩下滑就立刻放弃
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.66,0:17:33.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.30,0:17:34.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.20,0:17:38.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为了能一直做自己喜欢的事  我相当努力
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.68,0:17:42.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以看着周围的人  我一直这么想
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.10,0:17:45.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,「我并不是抱着玩玩的心态」
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.85,0:17:47.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,「只要我自己能吹奏那就行了」
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.44,0:17:51.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我这是遭报应了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.35,0:17:54.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来看这个
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.56,0:17:58.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是全国大赛的主页
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.60,0:18:00.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看这
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.72,0:18:02.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,进藤正和…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.71,0:18:05.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看到这个唤起了我的欲望
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.50,0:18:08.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要能进全国大赛就能让他听见我的演奏
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.30,0:18:09.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.70,0:18:13.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,既然来了这里  那就无论如何都要前进下去
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.16,0:18:16.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想让全国都能听到我们北宇治的演奏
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.57,0:18:18.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.84,0:18:20.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我就直说了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.92,0:18:23.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不赞成你回来
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.98,0:18:25.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为对这个部没有益处
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.24,0:18:29.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一切都是为了自己的私欲
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.67,0:18:31.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其结果就是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.63,0:18:34.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这就是所谓的老天有眼吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.18,0:18:40.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉  占用了那么多时间
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.70,0:18:42.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,继续补习吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.75,0:18:43.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.97,0:18:46.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我喜欢明日香学姐吹奏的悠风号
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.94,0:18:50.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,集训时的早上  学姐你有一个人吹奏悠风吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.20,0:18:54.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听到那首曲子之后我就觉得
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.43,0:18:57.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我喜欢这个乐声
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.93,0:19:04.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那首曲子是进藤先生创作的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.47,0:19:09.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,曲谱写在了和悠风号一起送来的笔记本上
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.62,0:19:11.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你父亲的…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.88,0:19:18.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,或许我内心是希望你能否定那首曲子吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.70,0:19:21.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,希望你能把它贬得一文不值
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.80,0:19:23.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.40,0:19:26.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我超喜欢它的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.32,0:19:31.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那首曲子既温暖  又非常温柔
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.72,0:19:34.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想一直听下去
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.44,0:19:36.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,甚至想你现在就吹给我听
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.76,0:19:40.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,黄前
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.88,0:19:43.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你今天出人意料地积极呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.51,0:19:50.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明日香学姐你才是和平时不一样了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.73,0:19:55.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.30,0:19:57.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说得是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.62,0:19:57.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.34,0:20:01.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呐  我们去河边吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.00,0:20:03.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想要吹奏了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.22,0:20:05.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.22,0:20:16.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你一直都在这里吹奏吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.32,0:20:19.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夏天不会有很多石蛾吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.58,0:20:21.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有蚊子什么的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.91,0:20:22.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蚊子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.21,0:20:26.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是那种不太会被叮的体质
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.66,0:20:29.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,香织的话可能很招蚊子
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.56,0:20:33.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为香织的血一看就很美味不是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.05,0:20:37.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,会忍不住想上去咬一口
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.48,0:20:39.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.59,0:20:45.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你真的想听？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.28,0:20:46.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.26,0:20:53.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,黄前你真的很有悠风的感觉呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.84,0:21:01.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我一直觉得自己没有什么悠风的感觉
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.55,0:21:05.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以当我看到你的时候吓了一跳
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.48,0:21:10.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,竟然有人这么有悠风的感觉
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.57,0:21:12.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你这算夸我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.57,0:21:14.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在夸你哦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.00,0:21:16.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.18,0:21:20.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我才希望你能听听我的事
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.50,0:21:29.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那份笑容  是以往的明日香学姐不曾展露过的笑容
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.40,0:23:38.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后  下一首乐曲开始了
